Description: Bundles a synthesised motor-insurance portfolio
    ('motor_portfolio') and matching loss-development cube ('motor_losses'),
    plus a multi-page 'blockr' example workflow that uses them. The
    underlying data is derived from 'insuranceData::dataCar' (de Jong &
    Heller, 2008) and 'ChainLadder::MW2014' (Wuthrich & Merz, 2014); a
    multi-insurer / multi-year dimension is synthesised on top so the
    example can demonstrate cross-filtering, KPIs, drilldowns, and a
    development triangle.
